Repeat: insert needle from below under the 3 loose strands of Rows 2, 3 and 4, and knit next st, bring st out under strands, p5
End Row: insert needle from below under the 3 loose strands of Rows 2, 3 and 4, and knit next st, bring st out under strands, p1, k1

Repeat: knit next st under 3 loose strands of Rows 10, 11 and 12, p5
End Row: knit next st under 3 loose strands of Rows 10, 11 and 12; p4, k1
